title: The Beatles - Love (Remix) Apple lossless files.zip
description:
An improved version of Beatle&#039;s Love album. Still a seamlessly flowing (gapless) album. Songs have been reordered with most of the more uptempo ones at the start. The ghastly Octopuses&#039; Garden is gone, as is some of the more self-indulgent bits that grate after repeated listenings. Some mainly instrumental links have been added and the occasional tasteful bit of speech and sound effects (all by The Beatles).
